sequenceDiagram
    participant N as 节点运营者
    participant C as NodeRegistry合约
    participant V1 as 验证者1
    participant V2 as 验证者2
    participant V3 as 验证者3

    N->>C: register(nodeInfo)
    C->>C: 创建提案 (proposalId)
    C-->>V1: 事件: NodeRegistered
    C-->>V2: 事件: NodeRegistered
    C-->>V3: 事件: NodeRegistered

    V1->>C: vote(proposalId, true)
    C->>C: 记录投票 (1/3)

    V2->>C: vote(proposalId, true)
    C->>C: 记录投票 (2/3)
    C->>C: 达到阈值，执行通过
    C-->>N: 事件: NodeApproved

    Note over C: 节点状态变为 Approved
